b'I was randomly looking at this picture today from my first (and I say first because I manifest that there will be more to come :smiling_face_with_smiling_eyes:) major international beauty campaign with L\xe2\x80\x99Oreal Paris and it made me thankful of some of the risks and chances I had taken in my life that ended up giving me opportunities like this. I always go back to the powerful words of Auntie @bettyirabor that\xe2\x80\x99s never left me about pushing yourself to do things even if you have to do it afraid. And Afraid I was then and still am even today with a lot of things but I do them anyway or atleast try. See I understand it\xe2\x80\x99s perfectly normal to be afraid of rejection or failure. But always head the words that They Biggest Risks bring The BIGGEST rewards.\xe2\x80\x9d To let\xe2\x80\x99s be real, Being told NO won\xe2\x80\x99t kill you. We are not salt that dissipates because of water. Rather sometimes a NO, a denial, a failure actually is a push forward in the right direction. So as hard as it may be to perceive NO differently and use it as a sword not a crutch, I urge you to try. I hope my random Thoughts today helps even if it\xe2\x80\x99s one person to gather the strength to take that bold step and start manifesting that dream that you always had. \n#tbt #randomthoughts #motivation #inspiration #truetalk #fearoffailure #fearofno #takechances #biggertheriskthebiggerthereward'

PRODUCTS
(*Note - These steps are after I thoroughly wash my face)

1. Rose water Toner -Loved using rose water as a toner for years. It\xe2\x80\x99s not as harsh as other toners I\xe2\x80\x99ve used and love the firmness of my skin after. I got this one from @dischem_pharmacies in SA. In Ghana try @gritpharmacy @jubenhseofbeauty 
2. Hyaluronic Acid - @reggies_makeovers introduced me to this product from @theordinary and Trust me it\xe2\x80\x99s a game changing product and affordable. I bought this one from @everythingbeautygh but you can look online also to purchase 
3. Aloe Vera Serum Face Masks - KEEP ON FOR 15mins! easy to use and very effective if you need that moisture. It\xe2\x80\x99s also great for all skin types. I prefer this for the aloe ingredient but try looking for other masks that give you the same result
4. EyeCream - The first sign of aging are the wrinkles and for me it started with my eyes. I was like helllll naaaaa! Once I started using eye cream religiously I started to see improvement and finer lines under my eyes. This one is Age Affect Eye and Lip Serum from @sorbetgroup 
5. Farsali SkinTune - This is actually a perfecting primer serum by @farsalicare and can you used with or without makeup. It blurs and mattifies your skin given it an even and smooth finish.
